author: mbautin
msg: [master] [hotfix] Moving the Snappy compression codec to the end of the list because we use enum ordinals in our persistent format

Summary: The Snappy change broke compatibility with the existing data because it added the Snappy codec in the middle of the enum, and we use ordinal numbers of the compression algorithm enum to store the compression algorithm in the HFile trailer.
